cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.NE 

The paper presents a new representation for deep learning with sparse 3D data, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). The focus on high resolution and memory allocation suggests a potential connection to graphics (cs.GR). Finally, the use of convolutional networks suggests a possible connection to neural networks (cs.NE).
